You need to provide 

- libglut
- libGL
- libGLU
- avifile (>= 0.60)

Just run 'make' to compile and './lesson35' to start.

The following hotkeys are supported:
 
 e 	toggles environment on/off
 b	toggles background on/off
 0,1,2	different effects
 q	quits program
  

